'''Mmasepala Setereke tša Overberg''' ke district wa [[Kapa Bodikela]].

=== Geography ===
Toropo kgolo kgolo ke [[Grabouw]] (pop. 21,593) in the Elgin Valley adjacent to the Hottentots-Holland on the north-western edge of the district. The municipal headquarters are located at [[Bredasdorp]] (pop. 12,749) in the southern part of the district. Other major towns are [[Swellendam]] (pop. 13,557) on the Breede River in the north-east, [[Caledon]] (pop. 10,650) in the western interior, and [[Hermanus]] (pop. 10,500) on the Atlantic coast.

